title: American Girl - Grace Sweet Shop
description:
Play Store URL: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.americangirl.gracesweetshop

Based on American Girl's 2015 Girl of the Year Grace Thomas, players take the role of Grace as she serves pastries and delicacies to guests, inspired by her trip to Paris.

To learn more about American Girl, or to find more fun games and activities, visit americangirl.com/play.
